videos.description: Jay Williams and Seth Greenberg express their opinions on why Grayson Allen should be suspended for tripping a player during Duke's game against Elon. Williams calls for a five-game suspension.

videos.description: Duke coach Mike Krzyzewski reacts to Grayson Allen tripping an Elon player in the first half.

videos.description: Grayson Allen receives a technical foul for tripping Elon's Steven Santa Ana in Duke's 72-61 win. The Blue Devils improve to 12-1 on the season with the victory.
videos.headline: Allen's technical causes controversy in Duke's win over Elon

videos.description: Grayson Allen is emotional when addressing the media after tripping Elon's Steven Santa Ana, saying he apologized after the game and doesn't see this behavior continuing.
